// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0360 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: e3c85343-e633-5cfe-9363-5ac108b78d1e

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*cbl-mariner:2.0*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:20.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:20.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:22.04*")
